  "page": "Mory",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Mory</b> is a place in the <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">riverlands</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#House_of_the_Dragon\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">House of the Dragon</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mory&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mory&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Pate_of_Mory\" title=\"Pate of Mory\">Pate of Mory</a> is killed by the forces of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">House Lannister</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/War_of_the_Five_Kings\" title=\"War of the Five Kings\">War of the Five Kings</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mory&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Tom</b>: <a href=\"/index.php/Alyn\" title=\"Alyn\">Alyn</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Joth_Quickbow\" title=\"Joth Quickbow\">Joth Quickbow</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Little_Matt\" title=\"Little Matt\">Little Matt</a> and his sister <a href=\"/index.php/Randa\" title=\"Randa\">Randa</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Anvil_Ryn\" title=\"Anvil Ryn\">Anvil Ryn</a>. Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Ormond_(knight)\" title=\"Ormond (knight)\">Ormond</a>. Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Dudley\" title=\"Dudley\">Dudley</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/Pate_of_Mory\" title=\"Pate of Mory\">Pate of Mory</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Pate_of_Lancewood\" title=\"Pate of Lancewood\">Pate</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Lancewood\" title=\"Lancewood\">Lancewood</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Old_Pate\" title=\"Old Pate\">Old Pate</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Pate_of_Shermer%27s_Grove\" title=\"Pate of Shermer&#39;s Grove\">Pate</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Shermer%27s_Grove\" title=\"Shermer&#39;s Grove\">Shermer's Grove</a>. Blind <a href=\"/index.php/Wyl_the_Whittler\" title=\"Wyl the Whittler\">Wyl the Whittler</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/Maerie_(goodwife)\" title=\"Maerie (goodwife)\">Goodwife Maerie</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/Maerie_the_Whore\" title=\"Maerie the Whore\">Maerie the Whore</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/Becca_(baker)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Becca (baker)\">Becca</a> the Baker. Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Raymun_Darry\" title=\"Raymun Darry\">Raymun Darry</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Darry_(father_of_Raymun)\" title=\"Lord Darry (father of Raymun)\">Lord Darry</a>, young <a href=\"/index.php/Lyman_Darry\" title=\"Lyman Darry\">Lord Darry</a>. The <a href=\"/index.php/Harry_Rivers\" title=\"Harry Rivers\">Bastard of Bracken</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/Fletcher_Will\" title=\"Fletcher Will\">Fletcher Will</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/Harsley\" title=\"Harsley\">Harsley</a>. Goodwife <a href=\"/index.php/Nolla\" title=\"Nolla\">Nolla</a>—<br /><b>Sandor</b>: Enough. You're making noise. These names mean nothing. Who were they?<br /><b>Beric</b>: People. People great and small, young and old. Good people and bad people, who died on the points of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">Lannister</a> spears or saw their bellies opened by Lannister swords.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Tom_of_Sevenstreams\" title=\"Tom of Sevenstreams\">Tom of Sevenstreams</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Sandor_Clegane\" title=\"Sandor Clegane\">Sandor Clegane</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Beric_Dondarrion\" title=\"Beric Dondarrion\">Beric Dondarrion</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"House_of_the_Dragon\">House of the Dragon</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mory&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: House of the Dragon\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>In the television adaptation <i><a href=\"/index.php/House_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"House of the Dragon\">House of the Dragon</a></i>, Mory is specified to belong to <a href=\"/index.php/House_Bracken\" title=\"House Bracken\">House Bracken</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rhbohotds02e05.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rhbohotds02e05.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Mory&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_34\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 34\">Chapter 34</a>, Arya VI.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rhbohotds02e05.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rhbohotds02e05.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/House_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"House of the Dragon\">House of the 